Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.00,English,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ken Libbrecht is the snowflake guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.93,English,,0,0,0,,- I was the snowflake consultant for the movie, "Frozen."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:25.55,English,,0,0,0,,It's okay to conjure snowflakes out of your fingertips,
