Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:51.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:57.23,English,,0,0,0,,- So, are you kind of like a snowflake artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:57.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.52,English,,0,0,0,,- I call it a designer snowflake.
