Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.49,English,,0,0,0,,I don't have a computer that does all this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.95,English,,0,0,0,,I just do it by hand, so every one's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:29.09,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Ken knows so much about snowflakes,
