Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:33.37,English,,0,0,0,,he can design and construct them to his own specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:33.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.27,English,,0,0,0,,- [Ken] So what's happening now is it's growing
