Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.11,English,,0,0,0,,Boy, these are just,  bang, just crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.36,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] The first close-up photograph of a snowflake
