Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.09,English,,0,0,0,,that no two snowflakes are alike, and he would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:29.37,English,,0,0,0,,Over the course of his life,
