Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.95,English,,0,0,0,,a selection of which appear in his book, "Snow Crystals,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.40,English,,0,0,0,,which is still in print today.
