Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.37,English,,0,0,0,,They're one in a million, I mean, literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.19,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] We are all so used to seeing pictures like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.99,English,,0,0,0,,that we are blind to the mysteries of the snowflake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:18.11,English,,0,0,0,,Like, why do they all have six fold, radial symmetry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:18.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
