Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.35,English,,0,0,0,,nobody asks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.01,English,,0,0,0,,Every time I give a talk, people are like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:15.11,English,,0,0,0,,"What are you doing? What on earth is this for?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:15.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.09,English,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the real reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.33,English,,0,0,0,,the real reason that I got into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.09,English,,0,0,0,,You look at a snowflake and you kind of go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.57,English,,0,0,0,,"Um, actually,  we don't have any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.56,English,,0,0,0,,"how that works."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.90,English,,0,0,0,,Well, that doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.86,English,,0,0,0,,We have to know how that works, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.70,English,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to be the guy
